<emphasis box="[281,472,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="557">Palpomyia auakua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[478,558,1944,1968]" pageId="7" pageNumber="557">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[478,558,1944,1968]" pageId="7" pageNumber="557" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, female. A. Flagellomeres, lateral view; B. Palpal segments 3–5; C. Femur and tibia of fore leg, lateral view; D. tarsal segment 5 of hind leg, lateral view. Scale bars: A= 0.64 mm; B, D= 0.04 mm; C= 0.16 mm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5224045" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5224045" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5224045/files/figure.png" pageId="8" pageNumber="558" startId="8.[151,250,1943,1967]" targetBox="[286,1311,198,1907]" targetPageId="8">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1436,1943,2004]" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,277,1943,1967]" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">FIGURE 6.</emphasis>
Female abdomens (A, C−D) and male genitalia (B). A. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Grogan &amp; Wirth" authorityYear="1979" box="[871,1057,1944,1968]" class="Insecta" family="Ceratopogonidae" genus="Palpomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="558" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aspina">
<emphasis box="[871,1057,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">Palpomyia aspina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, dorsal view; B. 
<taxonomicName authorityName=": Grogan &amp; Wirth" authorityYear="1975" box="[1240,1372,1944,1968]" class="Insecta" family="Ceratopogonidae" genus="Palpomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="558" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="subaspera">
<emphasis box="[1240,1372,1944,1968]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">P. subaspera</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, male genitalia, ventral view; C−D. 
<taxonomicName authority="Huerta &amp; Spinelli, 2021" authorityName="Huerta &amp; Spinelli" authorityYear="2021" box="[452,552,1980,2004]" class="Insecta" family="Ceratopogonidae" genus="Palpomyia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="558" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="auakua" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis box="[452,552,1980,2004]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">P. auakua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[558,639,1980,2004]" pageId="8" pageNumber="558">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[558,639,1980,2004]" pageId="8" pageNumber="558" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
, ventral view. Scale bars: A, C= 0.5 mm; B, D= 0.1 mm.
</paragraph>
